{"type":"article_comment","id":434206,"parentType":"article","parentId":21060,"uid":52847,"contents":"Anthropoid 类人猿行动：<a href=\"http://www.wenzhangba.com/zhuanti/erzhan/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">二战</a>期间，英国<a href=\"http://www.wenzhangba.com/zhuanti/qingbao/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">情报</a><a href=\"http://www.wenzhangba.com/zhuanti/jigou/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">机构</a>组成“类人猿”行动<a href=\"http://www.wenzhangba.com/zhuanti/xiaozu/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">小组</a>，<a href=\"http://www.wenzhangba.com/zhuanti/cehua/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">策划</a>并实施对<a href=\"http://www.wenzhangba.com/zhuanti/nacui/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">纳粹</a>盖世太保头目莱因哈德海德里希的刺杀<a href=\"http://www.wenzhangba.com/zhuanti/huodong/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">活动</a>，1942年5月27日，行动组情报<a href=\"http://www.wenzhangba.com/zhuanti/renyuan/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">人员</a><a href=\"http://www.wenzhangba.com/zhuanti/shiyong_5/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">使用</a>一枚将人肉毒杆菌<a href=\"http://www.wenzhangba.com/zhuanti/dusu/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">毒素</a>装入反坦克手榴弹内的<a href=\"http://www.wenzhangba.com/zhuanti/shengwu/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">生物</a>毒剂弹在海德里希当天活动的必经之路处将其炸伤，肉毒杆菌毒素进入他的体内后不久暴毙，<a href=\"http://www.wenzhangba.com/huati/chenggong/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">成功</a>刺杀，也使海德里希成为二战<a href=\"http://www.wenzhangba.com/zhuanti/shiqi/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">时期</a>被盟军刺杀的<a href=\"http://www.wenzhangba.com/zhuanti/zuigao/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">最高</a>军衔的纳粹将领 滚滚长江东逝水啊，不是所有英雄都能<a href=\"http://www.wenzhangba.com/zhuanti/quanshen/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">全身</a>而退，这群前捷克斯洛伐克的“狼牙山<a href=\"http://www.wenzhangba.com/zhuanti/zhuangshi/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">壮士</a>”们谱写的这段<a href=\"http://www.wenzhangba.com/huati/zhenshi/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">真实</a>历史被这部<a href=\"http://www.wenzhangba.com/zhuanti/yingpian/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">影片</a>讲述的着实是义薄云天、<a href=\"http://www.wenzhangba.com/huati/dangqihuichang/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">荡气回肠</a>。 复古<a href=\"http://www.wenzhangba.com/zhuanti/fengge/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">风格</a>的<a href=\"http://www.wenzhangba.com/zhuanti/zhizuo/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">制作</a>走心，各种<a href=\"http://www.wenzhangba.com/zhuanti/changjing/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">场景</a>、<a href=\"http://www.wenzhangba.com/zhuanti/daoju/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">道具</a>、<a href=\"http://www.wenzhangba.com/zhuanti/fuzhuang/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">服装</a>、化妆等都<a href=\"http://www.wenzhangba.com/huati/yisibugou/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">一丝不苟</a>，英文<a href=\"http://www.wenzhangba.com/zhuanti/duibai/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">对白</a>全部带上欧洲<a href=\"http://www.wenzhangba.com/zhuanti/kouyin/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">口音</a>，这个不知道是不是史实，不过派出的捷克特工确实是英国来的，全片没有太多的大<a href=\"http://www.wenzhangba.com/zhuanti/changmian/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">场面</a>来<a href=\"http://www.wenzhangba.com/zhuanti/biaoxian/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">表现</a><a href=\"http://www.wenzhangba.com/zhuanti/jinzhang/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">紧张</a>，而是用<a href=\"http://www.wenzhangba.com/huati/bolanbujing/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">波澜不惊</a>的<a href=\"http://www.wenzhangba.com/zhuanti/shoufa/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">手法</a>展示暗涌的行动<a href=\"http://www.wenzhangba.com/zhuanti/fengxian/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">风险</a>和随时将至的临头大祸，从而<a href=\"http://www.wenzhangba.com/huati/ganjue/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">感觉</a>显得更加真实 最<a href=\"http://www.wenzhangba.com/zhuanti/niubi/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">牛逼</a>的就是<a href=\"http://www.wenzhangba.com/zhuanti/biaoyan/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">表演</a>了，真是帅到<a href=\"http://www.wenzhangba.com/zhuanti/tianji/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">天际</a>了word墨菲<a href=\"http://www.wenzhangba.com/zhuanti/xiaoge/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">小哥</a>，老早就路转粉了，因为墨菲演的<a href=\"http://www.wenzhangba.com/zhuanti/huairen/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">坏人</a><a href=\"http://www.wenzhangba.com/zhuanti/shizai/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">实在</a>是太抢眼，几年过来，<a href=\"http://www.wenzhangba.com/zhuanti/yanji/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">演技</a>更是老道，这片里演的<a href=\"http://www.wenzhangba.com/zhuanti/zhuxian/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">主线</a>特工，简直看的<a href=\"http://www.wenzhangba.com/zhuanti/renxin/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">人心</a>碎啊，每<a href=\"http://www.wenzhangba.com/huati/yanshen/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">一个眼神</a>、每一个<a href=\"http://www.wenzhangba.com/zhuanti/biaoqing/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">表情</a>、每一句对白，表现出的<a href=\"http://www.wenzhangba.com/zhuanti/chenzhou/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">沉着</a>、<a href=\"http://www.wenzhangba.com/huati/jiaolv/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">焦虑</a>、<a href=\"http://www.wenzhangba.com/huati/fennu/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">愤怒</a>、崩溃、疑心、<a href=\"http://www.wenzhangba.com/huati/jianding/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">坚定</a>、不屈，<a href=\"http://www.wenzhangba.com/zhuanti/wanquan/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">完全</a>是影帝<a href=\"http://www.wenzhangba.com/zhuanti/jibie/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">级别</a>的，不火没天理啊；50度<a href=\"http://www.wenzhangba.com/zhuanti/badao/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">霸道</a><a href=\"http://www.wenzhangba.com/zhuanti/zongcai/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">总裁</a>多南的男二号<a href=\"http://www.wenzhangba.com/zhuanti/yanchu/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">演出</a>也很<a href=\"http://www.wenzhangba.com/zhuanti/jingcai/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">精彩</a>，加上诸多戏骨的<a href=\"http://www.wenzhangba.com/zhuanti/peijiao/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">配角</a>演出，跟在看<a href=\"http://www.wenzhangba.com/zhuanti/wutai/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">舞台</a>剧似的，就是爽！ 钢锯岭 是怼正面的表现战争，这部 类人猿 则是<a href=\"http://www.wenzhangba.com/zhuanti/dianxing/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">典型</a>的谋略游击战，同样强力<a href=\"http://www.wenzhangba.com/member/article_add.php\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">推荐</a>！","date":"2020-07-08","agreeCount":0,"discussionCount":0}